node.text:
Chasing waterfalls 💦 We can post your photos in our account, follow the link in our bio: @planetfervor and we will select your pictures

With @douglassertao in Brazil, a @nature and world-famous waterfalls country. 💦

Located in Campo Novo do Parecis, a municipality in the state of Mato Grosso in the Central-West Region of Brazil, this vast @nature wonder is called the Salto Utiariti. With a fall of 85 meters, a curiosity is that the well formed by the falls has the shape of Brazil. 🇧🇷

What's the most impressive waterfall you've ever witness?

📽 @douglassertao
📍 Salto Utiariti Waterfall, Brazil
🎶 Waterfalls - TLC

node.text:
Chased by a giraffe! 😳🦒 Share your photos with us and we will post them in our account. Apply for a feature following the link in our bio: @planetfervor

“This young male giraffe was orphaned at a young age and hand reared until he was able to survive in his own and be released back into to wild. So although this may look like an angry charge, it’s just the giraffe “keeping up with the herd” that he imprinted on as a youngster.

The giraffe chase happened unexpectedly and we did not force this moment. We do not encourage this type of interaction at all and in fact we avoid it at all costs so that the animal remains wild and free from human interaction. This was an unexpected and unavoidable moment.”

📽 @mattyardleyafrica
📍South Africa
